2009-09-21  Raphael 'kena' Poss  <r.c.poss@uva.nl>

	Add some demos with graphics.

	`checkers' - create a 8x8 checker board.	
	`mandel' - approximate the Mandelbrot set.

	* demo/checkers.c,
	* demo/mandel.c: New.

	* demo/Makefile.am: Update accordingly.

